    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> if we want to put the label on the right, how do we do?\n\nThat's why I suggest not putting the label in the widget at all, but keeping it in the external markup :)\n\nI think in the comments, we all converged to only adding a `selectId` option to the widget to add an `id` to the `select` (so you can manually link it to the `label` through `for`).\n",
